data.description: **OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY JANUARY 28th 2pm-4pm** Let's talk square footage. Need room to move? This home boast just under 3000 sq. ft., 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, office with an extra space upstairs. Currently being used as a second living room so you get 2 for the price of 1! Located in Creekside Manor near Abner Creek schools, Spartanburg district 5. The main floor features an open floor plan with large foyer, office, formal dining and kitchen/living room combo. Oh and don't forget the Sunroom! Still need more room? Head upstairs to find another area for a second living area or recreational room. Still wanting more room? Check out the Primary suite. Large room with ensuite bath with walk in closet. There is so much room in the closet, you could add a sitting area in the middle. Come see this one before it's gone. Plenty of room to stretch out in this one. The stove/range and dryer are plumbed for gas. TV mount stays with the home. Large candle decor will be removed prior to closing. Make it yours and schedule your showing today!
